➜冯巩戴生日帽庆63岁寿辰
http://www.sohu.com/a/436737231_255783	13793
<p><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201207/34991dbcac144f3c82059a630a176f1a.jpeg" /></p>
